# --- external-app stack (script 12: labwc + foot terminal + AppImage) ---
# Use codeberg RELEASE urls (path-named tllist-1.1.0.tar.gz), not /archive/ (bare
# 1.1.0.tar.gz) which script 12's `ls tllist-*.tar.*` glob would miss. labwc has
# no path-named release asset, so script 02 fetches it with --content-disposition.
https://codeberg.org/dnkl/tllist/releases/download/1.1.0/tllist-1.1.0.tar.gz
https://codeberg.org/dnkl/fcft/releases/download/3.3.1/fcft-3.3.1.tar.gz
https://codeberg.org/dnkl/foot/releases/download/1.21.0/foot-1.21.0.tar.gz
https://github.com/libfuse/libfuse/releases/download/fuse-3.16.2/fuse-3.16.2.tar.gz
https://github.com/labwc/labwc/archive/refs/tags/0.8.4.tar.gz

# --- fonts (shell uses "Noto Sans") — prebuilt hinted TTFs (the source repo has no .ttf) ---
https://github.com/notofonts/notofonts.github.io/raw/main/fonts/NotoSans/hinted/ttf/NotoSans-Regular.ttf
https://github.com/notofonts/notofonts.github.io/raw/main/fonts/NotoSans/hinted/ttf/NotoSans-Bold.ttf
https://github.com/notofonts/notofonts.github.io/raw/main/fonts/NotoSans/hinted/ttf/NotoSans-Italic.ttf
